第十一讲：财政决定外交的进退

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appAgMOhLAh7481/a_5bdc217985a49_7Y8pFL8l

<section style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 207.969px; padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app9lltoYxm7260/image/ueditor/72249100_1541153072.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="88397400_1541126160.jpg"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="text-align: center;">王陶陶，知名学者，国际问题专家。他个人经历颇为丰富，曾参与基层群众工作，统战工作，并参与数据情报分析和群体政治内参的工作。他善于从纷繁芜杂的历史表象中，直接抓住历史运行的本质规律，并用浅显易懂的语言向我们展示历史的原貌。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">王陶陶擅长进行政治局势判断，多次成功预测到“黑天鹅事件”。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">他相信，现代政治的本质在于群众政治，而真正能够理解群众政治者必须脱胎于大众，并对历史有深刻认知。通过学习他的内容，你可以掌握独立解读和评析历史事件和国际时事的方法论。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="height: 1px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(227, 223, 222);"></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0.7em; height: 0.7em; margin-right: 5px; margin-top: 0.5em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(246, 209, 179);"></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">课程简介</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;STHeiti STXihei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft JhengHei&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Tohoma, Arial; line-height: 28.8px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section 